    <p><a href="https://github.com/h8000572003/idea-value">GitHub</a>
     </a></p>
      <p>Two object assertions generate corresponding code:  in method block Enter ALT+ENTER ，Click [generate all  source1 assertion sources2]</p>
      <p>Two object assertions generate mapper code:   in method block Enter ALT+ENTER ，Click [generate all  source1 assertion sources2]</p>
      <p>object set value by name:select object Enter ALT+ENTER ，Click [generate all setters with name]</p>
